This is the configuration for twistedmatrix.com's mailman instalation.

It is adminstered using braid[1].

Mailman isn't directly installed, rather it uses the ubuntu's stock
installation of mailman.

It is available at the default location http://host/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo.

In production this is https://twistedmatrix.com/cgi-bin/mailman/listinfo.

install - Install mailman and update configuration.
dump:<dump-file>.tar - Dump mailing lists and archives
restore:<dump-file>.tar - Restore mailing lists and archives.
start - Start server.
stop - Stop server
restart - Restart server.

[1] https://github.com/twisted-infra/braid
